      "instruction": "<p>Add the <strong>chopped</strong> <strong>shallot</strong>, <strong>garlic</strong> and <strong>ginger paste</strong> to a <strong>food</strong> <strong>processor</strong> with your <strong>ground</strong> <strong>turmeric</strong>, <strong>curry</strong> <strong>powder</strong>, a small splash of <strong>water</strong> and a pinch of <strong>salt</strong></p><p>Blitz until smooth – this is your <strong>Thai-style yellow curry paste</strong></p>",
