    {
      "instruction": "<p>Boil half a kettle</p><p>Top, tail, peel and slice your <strong>carrot[s] </strong>into discs on the diagonal</p><p>Chop your <strong>creamed coconut </strong>roughly (if required!)</p><p>Chop your <strong>chicken</strong> <strong>breast</strong> <strong>strips</strong> into bite-sized pieces</p>",
