    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the chicken has browned, add your <strong>Thai-style</strong> <strong>yellow</strong> <strong>curry</strong> <strong>paste</strong> to the pan and cook for 2 min or until fragrant</p><p>Once fragrant, add the <strong>sliced</strong> <strong>carrot</strong> and <strong>coconut</strong> <strong>stock</strong> and bring to the boil</p><p>Once boiling, reduce the heat to medium-high and cook for 8-10 min or until the sauce has thickened and the chicken is cooked through (no pink meat!)</p>",
