    {
      "instruction": "<p>Whilst the chicken is cooking, slice your <strong>red chilli[es]</strong> into rounds</p><p>Once the chicken is cooked through, add the juice of <strong>half</strong> your <strong>lime[s]</strong> – this is your <strong>Thai-style yellow chicken curry</strong></p><p>Chop the <strong>remaining lime</strong> into 1 wedge per person</p>",
